This directory contains example configuration files:

 - aftr.conf - fully commented config file for an AFTR (OS independent)
 - aftr-script.freebsd - startup/shutdown script for a FreeBSD-based AFTR
 - aftr-script.linux - startup/shutdown script for a Linux-based AFTR

 - b4-openwrt/ - package files for an OpenWRT gateway-based B4
 - b4-freebsd/ - example files for a FreeBSD host-based B4
 - b4-ubuntu/ - example files for an Ubuntu host-based B4

 - shareone/ - config and script for an AFTR sharing a single public address

 - testbed/ - concrete examples from one of our testbeds
